<ttl id="1002J_S0010_72VAF_T004N" variety="T004N">
<name>SKID CONTROL BUZZER (w/ VSC)</name>
<para id="RM000001Q4L001X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="BC14N-02" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM000001Q4L001X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM000001Q4L001X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00000LN00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT SKID CONTROL BUZZER</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Apply battery negative voltage to terminal 1, and battery positive voltage to terminal 2 of the skid control buzzer, and then check that the buzzer sounds.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="F002192E03" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>The skid control buzzer sounds.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the skid control buzzer does not sound, replace the skid control buzzer.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
